## 7. THEME MANAGEMENT (DARK / LIGHT)

- Theme managed via **GetX** with a global `ThemeController`.
- User choice persisted with **GetStorage**.
- Theme changes via `Get.changeTheme(...)`; no app restart.

```dart
class ThemeController extends GetxController {
  final _isDark = false.obs;
  bool get isDark => _isDark.value;

  void toggleTheme() {
    _isDark.toggle();
    Get.changeTheme(isDark ? AppTheme.dark : AppTheme.light);
    // Persist to GetStorage
  }
}
```

